When designing or implementing UI components, use shadcn components as the foundation.

Reference these design systems for consistency:
https://nyxbui.design/
https://21st.dev/?tab=components
Always prefer composition over inheritance when building components.
Styling should be done with Tailwind CSS using:
The cn() utility for conditional class merging (for nyxbui components the code might have ny, make it cn which is same)
class-variance-authority (cva) for component variants

